{"tid":1433024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去機場接機？ We can do this all day","createTime":"2019-08-08T11:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T14:47:28.000Z","uid":108201,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"36a1336eaa68d6abe0f91fea15b067563465b7a7","tid":1433024,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:23:16.000Z","msg":"警方指未來數天不同地區都會有集會，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但認為集會不應在香港國際機場舉辦。</span></span>香港國際機場是一個非常繁忙的地方，警方留意到有不少國家對香港作出旅遊警示，所以警方希望示威者不要嚇到來港旅遊的其他國家旅客。<br />\n<br />\n每日去機場同到港旅客講我們的五大訴求，Are you ready?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1xORt9X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1xORt9X.jpg&h=1a46498f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有些事情不是因為有了希望才堅持, 而是因為堅持才有了希望!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9stNMXi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9stNMXi.gif&h=f0cac2a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8af315c25d4430b35ae6ed7ca0cc3f2f8cbe3ddf","tid":1433024,"uid":276887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:23:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4cef9b74a9ca25ccefcec05c991c1105941bcd25","tid":1433024,"uid":26015,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:24:11.000Z","msg":"我來啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3f8be0e7b33f74e9c4562a8530e8a5cb3dba43","tid":1433024,"uid":276887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:25:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3b5147cf3470975b403960ca28c88389513e4f61","tid":1433024,"uid":108201,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:25:56.000Z","msg":"每日到機場接機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aec4d742c8a8affc16d4eef83f4b549f65e384c","tid":1433024,"uid":272900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201